# 四、SRS算法（SM2）

数据

```
EF: easiness factor
interval
repetition
```

公式

```
if quality < 3:
    repetition = 0
    interval = 1
else:
    repetition += 1
    if repetition == 1:
        interval = 1
    elif repetition == 2:
        interval = 6
    else:
        interval = interval * EF

EF = EF + (0.1 - (5-quality)*(0.08+(5-quality)*0.02))
```

